is Arrow is a technology that provides support for developers, so the fact that I'm using

00:08:32.979 --> 00:08:38.020
Arrow should be mostly transparent to you, but to you, you shouldn't change anything,

00:08:38.020 --> 00:08:43.340
and in fact we're looking forward to Arrow because it should also give us some free features.

